---

---

<section id="about">
    <div class="container">
        <span class="section-label">// about</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">A little about me</h2>

        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-text">
                <p>
                    I'm a <strong>Computer Engineering</strong> student at the
                    <strong>University of Washington Bothell</strong>, based in Redmond, WA. I'm
                    passionate about building things that move, click, and occasionally explode.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Currently, I lead the <strong>simulation team</strong> at
                    <a href="https://github.com/TrickfireRobotics" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                        TrickFire Robotics</a
                    >, where we build simulation environments for Mars rovers using ROS&nbsp;2,
                    Gazebo, and Docker.
                </p>
                <p>
                    I love creative coding, cozy games, and cats. Always working on something
                    interesting.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-details">
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <span class="detail-icon">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path>
                            <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    <div>
                        <span class="detail-label">Location</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">Redmond, WA</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <span class="detail-icon">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"></path>
                            <path d="M6 12v5c3 3 6 3 12 0v-5"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    <div>
                        <span class="detail-label">Education</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">UW Bothell / CE / Class of '29</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <span class="detail-icon">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    <div>
                        <span class="detail-label">GPA</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">3.8 / Dean's List</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .about-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 0.7fr;
        gap: 4rem;
        align-items: start;
    }

    .about-text p {
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        font-size: 1.02rem;
    }

    .about-text p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .about-text strong {
        color: var(--cream);
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .about-details {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.85rem;
    }

    .detail-card {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
        background: var(--bg-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        transition: all 0.35s ease;
    }

    .detail-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--border-hover);
        box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.08);
        transform: translateX(4px);
    }

    .detail-icon {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        line-height: 1;
        color: var(--violet);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .detail-label {
        display: block;
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .detail-value {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.93rem;
        color: var(--cream);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .about-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }
    }
</style>
